Dragon amulet
The Lizards have an amulet which enables you to control the dragon for a short time. You will need this amulet to continue your quest.
#subobj  1
Find the owner of the amulet
The Lizard who carries the dragon amulet busies himself with the training of his tame toads near the old quarry. The eastern road will lead you right there. Look out for another landmark, the broken cart near the hill.
#subobj  2
Kill the owner of the amulet
The Lizard won't give the amulet away, and the trained toads will make it impossible to steal it. The only way out is to kill the owner.
#subobj  3
Take the amulet
Search the corpse of the Lizard and take the amulet.
